## 3. Strategic Gap Analysis

| Value chain stage | Status | Implication |
|---|---|---|
| Intake & prioritization (criteria, AHP, scoring) | ✅ Built, sophisticated | No further investment in next 90 days |
| Planning (scheduling engine, Gantt, resources) | ✅ Built, deep | No further investment in next 90 days |
| **Execution truth (baseline, actuals, variance)** | ❌ **Missing** | **Phase 1 priority** |
| **Decision support (EVM, EAC, exec dashboards)** | ❌ **Missing** | **Phase 2 priority** |
| **Governance enforcement (CR, audit, alignment, risk)** | 🟡 DB groundwork only | **Phase 3 priority** |

The front and middle of the project value chain are over-built relative to the back half. Closing the back half along the thesis (truth + governance) is the singular focus of this PRD.

